Implementation is **complete and correct**. All static/fitness/runtime gates 
pass. Telemetry seam wired end-to-end with W3C trace context propagation. Rebase
correctly integrated applied-key idempotency guard with telemetry span 
lifecycle. No architecture debt, no dropped guards, no broken spans.

